# vpypi

**vpypi** is a CLI tool to verify [GPG](https://gnupg.org/) signature for Python packages on [PyPI](http://pypi.org/).

## Installation

```bash
python3 -m pip install --user vpypi
```

## Usage

```bash
$ python3.9 -m vpypi flask==1.1.1
{
